 creates a gap in the ground\nstate energy level of the system. In addition when the trapping potential is\nactive the presence of standing waves with arbitrary small norm does not permit\nsmall data scattering. Eventually some asymptotic results are also given.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Oct 2014 15:47:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 31 Jan 2015 12:37:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 25 Mar 2016 07:44:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-28"}
